window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>In the Raverran Empire, magic is scarce, and those born with power are strictly controlled - taken as children and conscripted into the Falcon Army. </b> </p> <p>Zaira has lived her life on the streets to avoid this fate, hiding her mage-mark and thieving to survive. But hers is a rare and dangerous magic, one that threatens the entire empire. </p> <p>Lady Amalia Cornaro was never meant to be a Falconer. Heiress and scholar, she was born into a treacherous world of political machinations. </p> <p><b>But fate has bound the heir and the mage. And as war looms on the horizon, a single spark could turn their city into a pyre.</b> </p> <p><i>The Tethered Mage</i> is the first novel in a spellbinding new fantasy series. </p>"; 
